    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of Siberia, particularly to that of any of the large number of small ethnic groups living in Siberia. Most engage either in reindeer herding or fishing, while some also hunt furbearing animals or farm and raise horses or cattle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
